  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Lead, kindly Light, amidst th'encircling gloom,"
    }, {
      "text" : "Lead Thou me on!",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "The night is dark, and I am far from home,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 13
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 23
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 28
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 37
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Lead Thou me on !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Keep Thou my feet; I do not ask to see",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 21
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 35
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "The distant scene; one step enough for me.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 12
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 19
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 29
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 2",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "I was not ever thus, nor prayed that Thou",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 15
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 25
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 37
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Shouldst lead me on;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 17
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I loved to choose and see my path; but now",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 11
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 22
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 29
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 39
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Lead Thou me on!"
    }, {
      "text" : "I loved the garish day, and, spite of fears,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 12
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 19
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Pride ruled my will",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 15
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Remember not past years !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 18
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 24
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 3",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "So long thy power hath blest me, sure it still",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 12
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 23
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 33
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Will lead me on.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 13
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "O'er moor and fen, o'er crag and torrent, till"
    }, {
      "text" : "The night is gone,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 13
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And with the morn those distant faces smile,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 24
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Which I have loved long since, and lost awhile.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      }, {
